===Format===
* '''Pre-Quarter Finals:''''' Nov 17th - 19th, 2024
** 64 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 32 invited team.
*** 32 from Open Qulifier.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 18 matches in 3 days.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 team from each group (Total 32 teams)}} advance to Quarter Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Quarter Finals:''''' November 20th - 22nd, 2024
** 32 teams, 3 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 8.
** Each group will play 9 matches in 3 days.
** Round-robin format.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 32 teams}} advance to Semi-Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Semi-Finals:''''' November 23rd - 25th, 2024
** 24 teams, 3 matchdays. 
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 8.
** Each group will play 12 matches in 3 days.
** Round-robin format.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} advance to the Grand Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' November 26th - 27th & December 8th, 2024
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).
*** Day 1 and Day 2 will be played Online.
*** Day 3 will be played Offline in {{FlagNoLink|in}} Chennai.

